    {
      "id": "18f4750c-f3ba-80dd-8ae7-ebf18a5b12e0",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "The authors introduce DBN for student modelling and test the performance of their algorithm on 5 distinct datasets, outperforming previous approaches.",
